{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, under the evaluation of Qwen-2-72B, GPT-4 maintained its high performance, with 276 cases favoring its specificity compared to 68 for humans.",
    "Other models like Gemma-2-9b, although performing well, did not reach the high preference levels observed for GPT-4 or Llama-3.1-70B.",
    "In the evaluation of human reviewers' inter-rater reliability for the criteria of accuracy and specificity, Fleiss' Kappa was utilized.",
    "The calculated Fleiss' Kappa value for accuracy was 0.307.",
    "For specificity, the Fleiss' Kappa value was slightly higher at 0.346."
  ]
}